description_data.value: ** RESERVED ** This candidate has been reserved by an organization or individual that will use it when announcing a new security problem. When the candidate has been publicized, the details for this candidate will be provided.

descriptions.value: Buffer Overflow vulnerability in TRENDnet AC1200 TEW-821DAP with firmware version 3.00b06 allows an attacker to execute arbitrary code via the adm_add_user action.
Vulnerabilidad de desbordamiento de búfer en TRENDnet AC1200 TEW-821DAP con versión de firmware 3.00b06 permite a un atacante ejecutar código arbitrario mediante la acción adm_add_user.
